SCIENTIFIC INFORMATION RETRIEVAL IN DEVELOPING COUNTRIES.
     
THE CENTRE DE RECHERCHE RETROSPECTIVE DE MARSEILLE HAS BEEN DEALING FOR 4
YEARS WITH ON-LINE SEARCHES ORIENTED TOWARDS DEVELOPING COUNTRIES. NORTH
AFRICA HAS BEEN MAINLY CONCERNED, AND THE EXPERIENCE OF THE CENTRE BUILT UP IN
2 WAYS' BY DOING WORKS BY MAIL EXCHANGE, THE SEARCHES BEING CONDUCTED IN
MARSEILLE, OR BY GOING ON THE SPOT DEMONSTRATING AND HELPING PEOPLE TO DEVELOP
THEIR OWN ON-LINE CENTRE.
